SELECT "t"."Nom", "t"."Prix", "t"."Id", "t0"."Name", "t0"."PizzaId", "t0"."IngredientId", "t0"."Id"
FROM (
    SELECT "p"."Nom", "p"."Prix", "p"."Id"
    FROM "Pizzas" AS "p"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "i"."Name", "p0"."PizzaId", "p0"."IngredientId", "i"."Id"
    FROM "PizzaIngredients" AS "p0"
    INNER JOIN "Ingredients" AS "i" ON "p0"."IngredientId" = "i"."Id"
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."PizzaId"

SELECT "t"."Nom", "t"."Prix", "t"."Id", "t0"."Name", "t0"."PizzaId", "t0"."IngredientId", "t0"."Id"
FROM (
    SELECT "p"."Nom", "p"."Prix", "p"."Id"
    FROM "Pizzas" AS "p"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "i"."Name", "p0"."PizzaId", "p0"."IngredientId", "i"."Id"
    FROM "PizzaIngredients" AS "p0"
    INNER JOIN "Ingredients" AS "i" ON "p0"."IngredientId" = "i"."Id"
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."PizzaId"

    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS "t"

FROM (

    FROM "Pizzas" AS "p"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "i"."Name", "p0"."PizzaId", "p0"."IngredientId", "i"."Id"
    FROM "PizzaIngredients" AS "p0"

    SELECT "p"."Id", "p"."Nom", "p"."Prix"
    FROM "Pizzas" AS "p"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "i"."Name", "p0"."PizzaId", "p0"."IngredientId", "i"."Id"
    FROM "PizzaIngredients" AS "p0"
    INNER JOIN "Ingredients" AS "i" ON "p0"."IngredientId" = "i"."Id"
) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."PizzaId"
ORDER BY "t"."Id", "t0"."PizzaId", "t0"."IngredientId"
